## Flow 1 — Auto-Update Application Status on Interview Pass

**Type:** Record-Triggered Flow  
**Object:** `Interview__c`  
**Trigger:** After Update  
**Condition:** `Result__c = 'Pass'`

### Logic
1. Get parent Application record.
2. Update `Application__c.Application_Status__c = \"Shortlisted\"`.

### Flow XML
```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<Flow xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <apiVersion>59.0</apiVersion>
    <label>Auto Shortlist on Interview Pass</label>
    <processType>AutoLaunchedFlow</processType>
    <start>
        <object>Interview__c</object>
        <recordTriggerType>Update</recordTriggerType>
        <triggerType>RecordAfterSave</triggerType>
        <filters>
            <field>Result__c</field>
            <operator>EqualTo</operator>
            <value><stringValue>Pass</stringValue></value>
        </filters>
        <connector><targetReference>Update_Application</targetReference></connector>
    </start>
    <recordUpdates>
        <name>Update_Application</name>
        <label>Update Application Status</label>
        <inputAssignments>
            <field>Application_Status__c</field>
            <value><stringValue>Shortlisted</stringValue></value>
        </inputAssignments>
        <inputReference>$Record.Application__r</inputReference>
    </recordUpdates>
    <status>Active</status>
</Flow>
```

