## 1. Welcome Candidate Template

### Subject
```
Welcome to Our Talent Network, {!Candidate__c.Name}!
```

### Body
```
Hi {!Candidate__c.Name},

Thank you for joining our talent network. We have received your profile and our recruiters will reach out as soon as a matching opportunity arises.

Skills on record: {!Candidate__c.Skills__c}

Best regards,
Recruitment Team
```

### Metadata XML
```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<EmailTemplate xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <available>true</available>
    <encodingKey>UTF-8</encodingKey>
    <name>Welcome Candidate Template</name>
    <subject>Welcome to Our Talent Network, {!Candidate__c.Name}!</subject>
    <type>text</type>
    <uiType>Aloha</uiType>
</EmailTemplate>
```

