## Email Alerts Configuration

| Alert | Object | Template | Recipients | Trigger |
|-------|--------|----------|------------|---------|
| `New_Application_Alert` | Application__c | New_Application_Template | Job Owner | On Insert |
| `Offer_Approved_Alert` | Offer__c | Offer_Approved_Template | Candidate, Recruiter | On Approval |
| `Offer_Rejected_Alert` | Offer__c | Offer_Rejected_Template | Recruiter | On Rejection |
| `Interview_Scheduled_Alert` | Interview__c | Interview_Scheduled_Template | Candidate | On Insert |
| `Application_Rejected_Alert` | Application__c | Application_Rejected_Template | Candidate | On Status Change to Rejected |

---

